    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced garlic</strong>, <strong>courgette batons </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1701776534419-x200.jpg",
