            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Add your<strong> blanched peas</strong> to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over them to refresh them</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1701776539811-x200.jpg",
