            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the courgette has softened, add the <strong>cooked linguine</strong> and<strong> creamy veg stock </strong>to the pan and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Squeeze in the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lemon[s] </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1701776545856-x200.jpg",
