            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove from the heat and stir through <strong>half</strong> your <strong>goats' cheese</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>mint </strong>(you’ll use the rest for garnish!) and the <strong>refreshed peas </strong>– this is your <strong>courgette, pea & goats' cheese linguine</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1701776550850-x200.jpg",
