            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1701776550850-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>courgette, pea & goats' cheese linguine</strong> and crumble over the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>goats' cheese</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>salad </strong>to the side and season with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>mint</strong>, <strong>lemon wedge </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
